IC TP-4056 is a 1A stand alone single lithium-ion battery charging module with 2 LED indicaters for the indication of charging and fully-charged.

DataSheet:-  
Input Voltage : 4-8V
Output Voltage : 4.2V
Output Charing Current: 1A (Max) (Adjustable through Rprog)

Rprog|Ibat
kÎ©	  mA
30	  50
20	  70
10	  130
5	    250
4	    300
3	    400
2	    580
1.66  690
1.5	  780
1.33	900
1.2	  1000

Advantages: 
1) Simple to use
2) Adjustable Current using single resistor as discussed above
3) Linear Charge
4) Small module

Disadvantages:
1) Max. Output is 4.2V 
2) Max. Input is 8V
3) Max. Charging Current is 1A.  
